'X Factor' Judges Houses: The Definitive Ranking Of 2015 Contestants, As Voted For By You The Huffington Post UK | By Ashley Percival 
With Judges's Houses just around the corner, talk has turned to which ' X Factor ' contestants will make the final 12 and earn a place on the live shows. MORE 'X FACTOR': Ghost Gives Simon The Willies At 'X Factor' Judges' Houses 
After the 24 hopefuls have sung for mentors Simon Cowell , Cheryl Fernandez-Versini , Nick Grimshaw and Rita Ora , for the first time ever, the judges will be revealing who has made it through in a special live edition of the show hosted by Caroline Flack and Olly Murs on Sunday. 
With the decision firmly out of the public's hands, we're asking YOU who really deserves a spot on the Saturday night stage. 
Vote for your favourite(s) by clicking on the arrows next to each contestant below, and as the count comes in, the top acts will climb the ranks to reveal who you think should make it through. Close 'X Factor' Judges' Houses 2015 of
